{"tid":2462101,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"知錯了 媽咪哥","createTime":"2021-03-25T19:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T20:23:24.000Z","uid":365394,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a1178abef207acc81a67dd00a7a7007661b21d","tid":2462101,"uid":365394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T19:48:01.000Z","msg":"成日聽人講老母麵燈係玩下姐 咪當佢神咁拜<br />\n我屌 隻baidu 2日跌60蚊 係佢開post前買落仆晒街<br />\n<br />\n屌咩 仲以為燈神係串下佢玩下 點知親自試左伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAtm冇隻頂得住<br />\n<br />\n知錯了 媽咪哥 <br />\n但唔信你燈得到Tesla 老母麵即管試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b69523644f428ecf5fd985b28902b1eb98cb6c6","tid":2462101,"uid":59570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T20:12:49.000Z","msg":"你以為佢係燈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一次就燈，一千次就係神<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢根本有內幕料大戶黎"},{"pid":"4a6f26024d9cd426674a60aff0ed203216285c41","tid":2462101,"uid":365618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T20:19:27.000Z","msg":"不可試探神<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84edf5646d9d286d652eb717b71ba5951a6bcc7a","tid":2462101,"uid":216012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T20:23:24.000Z","msg":"終於知錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}